# AI Interview Coach — Backend Environment Variables
# Copy this to .env and fill in your values. Never commit .env to git.

# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your GitHub Personal Access Token with GitHub Models access
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_pat_here

# ── Optional overrides ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
